7
00:00:16,730 --> 00:00:17,860
a comma.

8
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:20,930
Never enter commas or any other notation to separate thousands.

9
00:00:20,930 --> 00:00:25,850
If your answer is 12340, enter that in 1-2-3-4-0,

