12
00:00:31,090 --> 00:00:33,090
Never enter currency or percentage signs.

13
00:00:33,090 --> 00:00:35,140
Just enter the raw number.

14
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:37,760
We'll always allow some tolerance for these answers.

15
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:41,640
So, for example, if the answer is 12340,

16
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:48,490
we might allow a number as low as 12330 and as high as 12350.

17
00:00:48,490 --> 00:00:52,440
We'll always have a little bit of tolerance range in there.

18
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,330
